name: TC_03_02_01 | Verify navigation to Home page from fromFooterLogo
description: To verify that user can navigate to Home page from fromFooterLogo.
descriptionHtml: To verify that user can navigate to Home page from fromFooterLogo.

testStage.description: To verify that user can navigate to Home page from fromFooterLogo.

steps.name: Preconditions: Login as a registered user
Click on the Logo in Footer.
Verify user is redirected to Home page
Verify that Home page has "Millions of domains with the ultimate privacy protection" heading.
